{"pageProps":{"source":"<div class=\"space-y-4 whitespace-normal *:first:mt-0 *:last:mb-0\"><p><a class=\"\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://github.com/kopia/kopia\">Kopia</a> est un logiciel de sauvegarde disponible sur Windows, macOS et Linux.</p><h2>Initialiser un dépôt</h2><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">kopia repository create s3 --bucket=&lt;bucket&gt; --access-key=&lt;access_key&gt; --secret-access-key=&lt;secret_key&gt; --endpoint &lt;endpoint&gt;\n</code></pre></div><h2>Créer une sauvegarde</h2><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">kopia snapshot create &lt;dossier|fichier&gt;\n</code></pre></div><h2>Monter un dépôt</h2><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">kopia mount all &lt;dossier&gt;\nkopia mount &lt;snapshot_id&gt; &lt;dossier&gt;\n</code></pre></div><h2>Se déconnecter d&#x27;un dépôt</h2><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">kopia repository disconnect\n</code></pre></div><h2>Se connecter à un dépôt</h2><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">kopia repository connect s3 --bucket=&lt;bucket&gt; --access-key=&lt;access_key&gt; --secret-access-key=&lt;secret_key&gt; --endpoint &lt;endpoint&gt;\n</code></pre></div><h2>Lister les sauvegardes</h2><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">kopia snapshot list\n</code></pre></div><h2>Lister les fichier d&#x27;une sauvegarde</h2><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">kapia ls -l &lt;snpashot_id&gt;\n</code></pre></div><h2>Supprimer une sauvegarde</h2><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">kopia snapshot delete &lt;snapshot_id&gt; --delete\n</code></pre></div><h2>Changer le type de compression</h2><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">kopia policy set --global --compression=pgzip\n</code></pre></div></div>","isIndex":false,"file":"Kopia.md","fileName":"Kopia","title":"Kopia","comments":true,"permalink":"kopia","datePublished":"2021-06-07T20:36","dateUpdated":"2021-06-07T20:36","publish":true,"rss":true,"note":"54"},"__N_SSG":true}